                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 891.001.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of the United States</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Shah of Persia</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-09-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 23, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have received with profound regret the announcement of the death, on September
                    22, of His Imperial Highness the Regent.</p>
                <p>I convey to you my sincere condolence.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Taft.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
